that he doesn't ask any questions

13:08.496 --> 13:09.955
- about the actual software.
- Oh, I love

13:10.039 --> 13:11.457
how you're assuming it's a he.

13:11.540 --> 13:12.958
I know what you're thinking!

13:13.042 --> 13:15.085
Look who's back.

13:15.169 --> 13:18.255
After your father
unceremoniously let me quit.

13:18.464 --> 13:20.591
