on the third floor without so much

13:20.674 --> 13:22.802
as a "feel free
to use the third floor" joke.

13:22.885 --> 13:25.304
Anyway...

13:25.387 --> 13:28.057
what are you two doing down here
after a long mid-weekend?

13:28.140 --> 13:30.518
Well, Dad said we could use
the offices for Fakeblock.

13:30.726 --> 13:33.145
He actually said,
"Feel free to use the third floor."

13:33.354 --> 13:36.065
Mm. Now I'm glad I gave
one of those offices away.

13:36.232 --> 13:38.943
- You gave an office away?
- Well, just one of the smaller ones.

13:39.026 --> 13:40.778
You won't even know
it's being used.

13:40.861 --> 13:43.489
...because an actor's body
is his instrument.

13:43.572 --> 13:45.366
Come get my shower ready
and then take over

13:45.449 --> 13:47.117
- on the elliptical.
- I'm on it. I got it.

13:47.326 --> 13:49.161
No, you can't take another shower.

13:49.245 --> 13:52.456
I'm still in socks,
and I'm about to serve food.

13:52.540 --> 13:53.624
Well, what's for dinner?

13:53.707 --> 13:55.668
Turkey jerky, popcorn,

13:55.751 --> 13:59.380
- and leftover Jeff.
