13:59.463 --> 14:00.881
You know, I don't want to jinx it,

14:00.965 --> 14:03.551
but this certainly is better
than living in that attic, yes?

14:03.634 --> 14:05.052
- Oh, definitely.
- It's so great, Dad.

14:05.302 --> 14:06.929
And what's our number one rule?

14:07.012 --> 14:08.472
Don't tell Michael.

14:08.556 --> 14:12.476
Well, yes, but I also meant, 88 more days,
