Yeah, I think I'm in the wrong place.

19:06.270 --> 19:08.480
- I was looking for a guy named Tony.
- No, Mr. Bluth.

19:08.564 --> 19:11.441
You're exactly in the right place.
Take a seat.

19:11.525 --> 19:13.569
No, yeah, you know what? I... I'm fine.

