on your coming out.

19:16.613 --> 19:18.490
So brave.

19:18.907 --> 19:20.534
- So brave.
- So brave.

19:20.617 --> 19:21.952
So brave. But you know what?
Thank you. It's...

19:22.035 --> 19:23.495
- The struggle is...
- Oh, shut up.

19:23.579 --> 19:26.248
We know you're as straight
as an Oklahoma highway.

