No, no, no. I'm... I'm gay.

19:55.027 --> 19:57.154
Yeah, sure, because of your trick.

19:57.237 --> 20:01.658
<i>Gob had recently performed</i>
<i>a sexuality switch illusion at a parade.</i>

20:01.742 --> 20:06.580
<i>It ended unexpectedly when his partner
had a premature emulsification.</i>

20:06.997 --> 20:09.499
<i>This left Gob
publicly out of the closet...</i>

20:09.833 --> 20:11.335
Who's straight now?

20:11.418 --> 20:12.669
<i>...with no way back in</i>

20:13.253 --> 20:15.005
<i>and a sexual identity</i>

20:15.088 --> 20:17.674
