from undoing.</i>

20:17.758 --> 20:19.843
Well, that son of a buck
gonna have to stay gay.

20:19.927 --> 20:21.970
Unfortunately for you,
we also caught your appearance

20:22.054 --> 20:23.889
on that religious program

20:23.972 --> 20:28.060
<i>And As It Is Such, So Also</i>
<i>As Such It Is...</i> what is it?

