doing the hurting.

20:57.965 --> 21:01.260
Oh, right, then there'd be less gays
that would suck the gays out.

21:01.343 --> 21:02.803
- No.
- I mean, off.

21:02.886 --> 21:05.097
Because it's a destructive sham
that thinks

21:05.180 --> 21:08.183
that homosexuality can be cured
through shame and fear,

21:08.600 --> 21:10.477
you pathetic little dipshit.

21:11.478 --> 21:12.688
You're right, I hear you.

21:12.771 --> 21:15.941
And I'll cancel my appointment.
I'll lose my deposit, but right is right.

21:16.024 --> 21:18.735
It's too late for that. You said on TV

21:18.819 --> 21:20.404
you're going into conversion therapy,

21:20.487 --> 21:21.947
so you are going to go.

21:22.030 --> 21:24.408
And then you're going
to announce it didn't work.

21:25.742 --> 21:28.537
So... I have to stay gay?

21:28.829 --> 21:31.373
Just for seven years.
Then we'll let you age out.

21:31.873 --> 21:33.959
It's a lot more generous than what I did

21:34.042 --> 21:35.502
to that last guy
who faked being gay.

21:35.752 --> 21:37.754
You know him. Your pal Tony Wonder.

21:38.422 --> 21:40.924
Don't worry. We took care of him.
Didn't we, boys?

21:41.174 --> 21:42.801
- We sure did.
- We sure did.

21:42.884 --> 21:45.262
Now, do as you're told,
and you will have made

21:45.345 --> 21:47.306
some very powerful friends.

21:48.015 --> 21:51.018
- In case you ever need a favor.
- Austero.

