22:05.532 --> 22:07.701
my brother probably
didn't have anything to do

22:07.784 --> 22:10.245
with your sister's disappearance.

22:10.912 --> 22:12.039
I'm not worried about it.

22:12.539 --> 22:14.833
To be honest, we fought all the time,

22:14.916 --> 22:17.419
so it's probably better
for our relationship

22:17.502 --> 22:19.504
that she's no longer around.

