22:31.224 --> 22:33.226
you will always be loyal to us.

22:36.480 --> 22:38.065
Since you're so good at magic,

22:38.148 --> 22:40.067
why don't you
make that disappear.

22:44.237 --> 22:45.572
Is that what I think it is?

22:45.655 --> 22:47.616
- Yes, it's what you think it is.
- Yeah.

22:47.699 --> 22:49.576
We got as much of the cement off
as we could.

22:49.659 --> 22:51.620
Don't need it traced back to us.

22:52.496 --> 22:53.622
You mention this to anyone,

22:53.705 --> 22:55.916
and this is the last sound
you're going to hear.

22:55.999 --> 23:00.087
You're gonna... tap-dance on <i>my </i> grave?

23:01.880 --> 23:05.300
Oh, hell, you saw the matinee.
Out you go.

23:05.634 --> 23:07.803
Chop-chop. I want it off my floor

23:07.886 --> 23:09.346
and somewhere
